  <brief_title>Effectiveness of Antibiotic Prophylaxis for Totally Implantable Venous Access Device</brief_title>
  <acronym>TIVAD</acronym>
  <official_title>A Randomized, Double-blind, Placebo-controlled Trial to Determine Effectiveness of Antibiotic Prophylaxis for Totally Implantable Venous Access Device.</official_title>
