  <eligibility>
    <criteria>
      <textblock>
        Inclusion Criteria:

          -  Older than 18 years of age

          -  Have solid tumor

          -  White cells &gt;4000

          -  Platelets &gt;100.000

          -  Prothrombin time in normal range

        Exclusion Criteria:

          -  Drug allergy

          -  Diabetes mellitus
      </textblock>
